description: 听两遍短文，然后根据所听内容和提示将所缺信息填写在相应位置上。你有1分钟的时间浏览提示信息。（听完录音后，请在90秒钟内将所缺信息输入到指定的答题区域。）

content.contentDesc:
Good morning, everyone. Welcome to People Park. First, you can take a free open-air bus to Animal Corner, our small and special zoo. Take a horse ride and enjoy the cute monkeys. This part of the park is right for all the family.

Leave Animal Corner and walk to your right. Here you will find the Summer Palace. Climb the towers to see a view of the park. When you have finished in the palace, you can go to the West, the street of a 19th century American town. Go into the bank, hotel and doctor's office. The restaurant has real food, and you can enjoy a hamburger before moving on. At 12 noon every day you can watch an exciting show in the street. Next stop is Lake Experience where you can go on a boat. Go on to the final stop, there is the Market of the East, a wonderful place to buy presents for all your friends.

Then the bus will return you back at 4 pm.

analysisList.text:
1. First, you can take a free open-air bus to Animal Corner, our small and special zoo.

  2. The restaurant has real food, and you can enjoy a hamburger before moving on.

  3. Go into the bank, hotel and doctor's office.

  4. Next stop is Lake Adventure where you can go on a boat.

  5. Then the bus will return you back at 4 pm.

description: 听录音，根据所听到的内容，记录关键信息。每段录音读两遍。

subContents.content:
Monday

Weather: It was __$$__ and __$$__.

Went to the __$$__ near our hotel.

We __$$__ paragliding and rode __$$__ to Georgetown.

Lunch: Malaysian yellow __$$__.


Tuesday

Weather: It was __$$__ hard.

Got to the top of hill by __$$__.

Lunch: One __$$__ of rice and some fish. Because we didn't bring __$$__ money.

analysisList.text:
I was on vacation with my family last week. We went to Penang in Malaysia. We arrived there on Monday morning. It was sunny and hot that day, so we went to the beach near our hotel. My sister and I tried paragliding. We had delicious Malaysian yellow noodles for lunch. We also rode bicycles to Georgetown that afternoon. It was so exciting!

But the next day was very different. My father and I decided to go to Penang Hill and wanted to walk up to the top, but then it started raining a little so we decided to take the train. When we got to the top, it was raining really hard. We were all wet and cold because we had no umbrellas. We couldn’t see anything below because of the bad weather. Without bringing enough money, we only had one bowl of rice and some fish for lunch. Luckily, the food tasted great.

description: 阅读下列短文，根据短文内容，从短文后各题所给的选项中，选择最佳选项。

content.content:
Louvre Museum (卢浮宫)
Opening hours

  • Monday, Thursday, Saturday, Sunday: from 9 a.m. to 6 p.m.

  • Wednesday, Friday: from 9 a.m. to 9:45 p.m.

  • Tuesday: closed

Free admission (免费入场)

  • Visitors under the age of 18

  • Old people from the European Economic Area (欧洲经济区)

  • Teachers of art and art history

  • Disabled (残疾的) visitors

Entrances (入口) to the museum

  • Pyramid and Galerie du Carrousel entrances: from 9 a.m. to 7:30 p.m.

  • Passage Richelieu entrance: from 9 a.m. to 5:30 p.m.

  • Porte des Lions entrance: This entrance may be closed for technical (技术的) reasons. Please call us the day before your visit at 40205317.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：Tuesday: closed 周二：关闭。

因此，正确答案是B。

subContents.content: Who can visit Louvre Museum for free?

options.option: Children from the European Economic Area.
Students of art and art history.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：Free admission (免费入场)；Disabled (残疾的) visitors 残疾游客。

因此，正确答案是D。

subContents.content: Which entrance to the museum may be closed for technical reasons?

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：Porte des Lions entrance: This entrance may be closed for technical (技术的) reasons. Porte des Lions entrance：此入口可能会因技术原因而关闭。

因此，正确答案是D。
